<div class="bg-gray-50">
<div class="embed-content">

<div class="tailwind-container">

  <link rel="stylesheet" media="all" href="https://ca-dmv.cityinnovate.com/assets/tailwind-container-39aff895a3508d7b01066cd260ee83c3354dbeec99448ffea0e90bc43de54a32.css" data-turbolinks-track="reload" />

  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto pt-12 pb-16 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:pt-20 lg:pb-14 lg:px-8">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-8">
        <div class="md:col-span-8">
          <div class="px-8 pt-12">
            <h4 class="text-2xl leading-8 font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight sm:text-3xl sm:leading-9">Challenge</h4>
            <div class="trix-content">
              The Department of  Motor Vehicles is seeking a solution to reduce processing time utilizing automation to sync many disjointed processes and systems into a single human resource management system that is accessible on any device for our DMV staff.
              <ul>
<li>
<a href="https://www.dmv.ca.gov/portal/file/vendor-day-2022-presentation-pdf/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CA  DMV Vendor Day2022 Presentation PDF </a> </li>
<li><a href="https://cadmv.webex.com/recordingservice/sites/cadmv/recording/playback/95a8dcc67240103abb3f00505681e149" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CA DMV Vendor Day 2022 Event Recording</a></li>
</ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="px-8 pt-12">
            <h4 class="text-2xl leading-8 font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight sm:text-3xl sm:leading-9">Background</h4>
            <div class="trix-content">
              <p style="margin-left:0in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Human Resources staff are working with manual and often inefficient and ineffective processes. HR does not have true position control and suffers from a lack of ability to correctly track positions and appropriately connect criteria to position numbers. HR also lacks many self-service capabilities including digital forms, workflow, and tracking. .</span></p><p style="margin-left:0in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Ideas being considered:</span></p><ul>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">In-house electronic recruitment solution</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Use of “bot” technology to re-key and transfer data to a variety of systems</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Front end band-aids that cause additional work on the back end</span></li>
</ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="px-8 pt-12">
            <h4 class="text-2xl leading-8 font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight sm:text-3xl sm:leading-9">Requirements & Outcome</h4>
            <div class="trix-content">
              <p>Desired Outcomes:</p><ul>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">HR compliance</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Improved productivity and efficiency</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Improved employee experience</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Improved reporting functionality</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Automated intake and processing (versus manual).</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Seamless integration with multiple internal and external applications</span></li>
</ul><p><span style="color:#414041;">Priorities:</span></p><ol>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Position Control</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Onboarding/Offboarding</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Appraisal Tracking</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Succession/Workforce Planning</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Self Service</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Service Tracking</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Case Management</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Employee Engagement</span></li>
<li><span style="color:#414041;">Enrichment</span></li>
<li>Recruitment </li>
</ol><p>Points to ponder: </p><ul>
<li style="margin-left:.19in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Immediate need to act</span></li>
<li style="margin-left:.19in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Current processes are manual (via desktop tools usually like spreadsheets)</span></li>
<li style="margin-left:.19in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Transactions must interface with SCO, CalPERS, Oracle, Fi$Cal etc.</span></li>
<li style="margin-left:.19in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Time tracking implementation in progress</span></li>
<li style="margin-left:.19in;"><span style="color:#414041;">Payroll solution is not needed</span></li>
<li style="margin-left:.19in;"><span style="color:#414041;">IT onboarding solution in progress</span></li>
</ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-4">

        <div class="px-8 py-12 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white mt-12">



